<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WorkSpy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: white; /* Light background color */
        }

        /* Header Styling */
        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center; /* Vertically center items */
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #3B7A57; /* Green */
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333; /* Dark border */
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 32px; /* Increased font size for logo */
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #F26D5B; /* Yellow for logo */
        }

        .logo span {
            margin-top: -20px;
            font-size: 18.5px; /* Smaller font size for "WorkSpy" */
            color: #f0f0f0; /* Light gray for WorkSpy */
        }

        nav a {
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #f0f0f0; /* Light grey for better contrast */
            font-weight: 600;
            position: relative;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #F26D5B; /* Highlight color for hover */
        }

        /* Header Link Hover Animation */
        nav a::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 300%;
            height: 300%;
            background-color: #F26D5B;
            border-radius: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s, width 0.4s, height 0.4s;
        }

        nav a:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
        }

        /* Main Content Styling */
        .content {
            display: flex;
            padding: 50px;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 40px;
            justify-content: center; /* Centers the content */
        }

        .content img {
            width: 50%;
        }

        .text-content {
            max-width: 50%;
        }

        .text-content h1 {
            font-size: 56px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #000; /* Black for the heading */
        }

        .text-content h1 span {
            color: #F26D5B; /* Yellow for emphasis */
            display: inline-block;
            background: transparent; /* Light grey background */
            padding: 0 5px;
            border-radius: 5px; /* Rounded background */
        }

        .text-content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #333; /* Dark grey for readability */
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #3B7A57; /* Green */
            color: #F26D5B; /* Yellow for button text */
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 2px solid #FFF;
            border-radius: 5px; /* Rounded button */
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Button shadow */
            transition: background-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; /* Smooth hover effect */
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #3B7A57; /* Darker green */
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* WORKSPY Title Styling */
        .workspy-title {
          display: inline-block; /* Makes the border only around the text */
          font-size: 100px;
          margin-left: 55px;
          font-weight: 800;
          color: #F26D5B;
          text-align: center;
          margin-top: 50px;
          text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(2, 74, 44, 0.7);
          border: 4px solid #3B7A57; /* Green border */
          border-radius: 15px; /* Rounded corners for the border */
          padding: 10px; /* Adds space between the text and border */
          font-family: 'Lobster', cursive; /* New font */
          }

        /* Footer Styling */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #3B7A57; /* Green footer */
            color: #FFF;
            font-size: 14px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            WS 
            <span>"Empowering Workforces, Simplifying Lives"</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/login" class="btn">LOGIN</a> <!-- Login button -->
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <div class="content">
        <!-- Image URL input section -->
        <img id="mainImage" src="https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/new-team-members-concept-illustration_114360-7501.jpg?t=st=1732735530~exp=1732739130~hmac=1a325e9f994bd593509b391d5650bacd8cf2842c586e9a3747df37b260e34c7b&w=996" alt="Illustration">
        <div class="text-content">
            <div class="workspy-title">
                WORKSPY
            </div>

            <h1>Collaborate with team, & <span>achieve</span> best work</h1>
            <p>-Team tasks at an organization can be a challenge, but clear goals, open communication, and expectations can lead to success and a tighter team-</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 WorkSpy. All rights reserved to 'M-A-L'.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
